    .dialog.success-package.none
        .hd-dialog
            .title-hd-dialog 提示
            .fork-hd-dialog
        .bd-dialog.radius
            h4.title-bd-dialog 已成功领取礼包！
            ul.l-package-dialog
                li.li-package-dialog
